Video - 1
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Single Video with Controls on Web Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Use of Video on Web Page Using HTML5</h1>
    <video src="sample-mp4-file.mp4" controls autoplay loop width="150" height="150">
        Your browser does not support the <code>video</code> element.
    </video>
</body>
</html>
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
