Video - 2 
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Video on Web Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Use of Multiple Video Files on Web Page Using HTML5</h1>
    <video controls autoplay width="100" height="100">
        <source src="sample-mp4-file.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        <source src="sample-ogv-file.ogg" type="video/ogg">
        <source src="sample-webm-file.webm" type="video/webm">
        Your browser does not support the <code>video</code> element.
    </video>
</body>
</html>
